# Every asdf-managed toolchain the repo needs, in one place. Install them all
# with `make install-tools` (adds any missing asdf plugin, then `asdf install`).
#
# Lines with more than one version: the first is the repo default; the extra is
# the older LTS the examples/ projects deliberately build against (each pins the
# exact version in its own examples/**/.tool-versions, which resolves here).
#
# Not asdf-managed, so not listed: Rust (rustup, via rust/rust-toolchain.toml)
# and Node (corepack, via "packageManager" in typescript/package.json).
